"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-katarina-johnson-thompson-finally-claims-first-olympic-medal-21396855\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"An emotionalKatarina Johnson-Thompsonsaid she was 'relieved' after the Team GB athlete finally claimed her first Olympic medal with silver in the heptathlon atParis2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson narrowly missed out on gold to the three-time Olympic champion Nafi Thiam despite the Belgian all the way across the two-day event.\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit needed to beat Thiam in the 800m by eight seconds and as KJT crossed the line in second the Belgian was a fair distance behind her.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Thiam just got over the line, with a couple of seconds to spare to keep hold of her Olympic title.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old, though, has won two World Championship golds and now can boast an Olympic silver on her fourth trip to the Games.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not even describe the words but I am just so relieved and so happy that I have an Olympic medal to add to my collection,' she told the BBC.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9944626571467359, \"rank\": 0.0055501842767682556, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was the only one I did not have and it's been so hard getting back to this point.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a phenomenal effort from KJT \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00ab\\u00b6A sensational silver in Paris \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u0088Nafi Thiam did enough to secure an historic third Olympic gold medal.#BBCOlympics#Paris2024#Olympicspic.twitter.com/vRfsac1dBC  'In the lead-up to these Games, all I have been saying is that's what I want, obviously I wanted a medal but I just wanted to have a chance at the start of the 800m and that's what I had.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999517087884, \"rank\": 4.829117648477685e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a very far-off chance - eight seconds - but that's what this sport is, it's about getting to this point and seeing whose got it at the end.'\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thiam has now won gold at the last threeOlympic Games, cementing the Belgian's place as one of her country's finest-ever athletes.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"score\": 0.9515712076831201, \"rank\": 0.025580524422573955, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medalist in 2000, Denise Lewis, said of Thiam: 'She's been incredible, because she's know the pressure that she'd be under to achieve this incredibly rare feat.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Denise Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Lewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We will never see another heptathlete quite like her, she is sensational.'\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:How does the heptathlon scoring system work as Katarina Johnson-Thompson eyes gold in Paris?\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999517087884, \"rank\": 4.829117648477685e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or